The recent earthquake in Turkey and Syria has left a trail of destruction and heartbreak. 💔 
Countless lives lost, homes destroyed and families torn apart. My heart aches for my beloved home country, Turkey, and all those affected by this tragedy. 
Both countries have been forever changed and the impact on the lives of those affected is immeasurable. The pain and suffering is beyond words.
The need for aid and support is great, and every little bit helps. I encourage you to join me in donating to one or more of these organizations working tirelessly to provide relief to those in need. 
Time is of the essence and every second counts for those still waiting to be rescued under the rubble in freezing temperatures. Let's do our part and bring hope to those in need. #Earthquake #Turkey #Syria #Deprem #Donate #EarthquakeRelief #HelpTurkey #HelpSyria

Earthquakes, corrupt governments, mass shootings, war, collective trauma… 🥀 
In a world filled with chaos and uncertainty love remains the one constant that can heal the deepest wounds and bring hope for a brighter tomorrow. It may not be able to fix all the problems in the world but it definitely gives us the strength and resilience to face them with compassion, kindness and empathy for one another. Whether with our partners, family, or friends, let us cherish the love that surrounds us and spread it to those who may need it the most. ❤️‍🩹

People often ask me how I handle my workload. The answer is simple: @upwork 
As an entrepreneur juggling multiple businesses, I have to do a LOT, but I don’t have to do it ALL. 
With @Upwork, I can connect with the right talent from all over the world whether it’s a graphic designer, a web developer, a writer, or even an accountant. 
So, if you’re in a similar boat and could use some extra help use Upwork now to find talented professionals from around the world for all of your business needs! 
Learn more via the link in bio. ⬆️ 
#UpworkPartner #EntrepreneurLife
